LARAVEL APP DIRECTORY 

1) ROUTES:
-- app -> routes -> web.php : Were all your page web app page routes goes:
	
	//Example: IF user visit the home page go to the view (Located in app -> resources ->views->welcome.blade.php)
	Route::get('/', function () {
    	return view('welcome'); 
	});


2) RESOURCES:
	VIEWS:
		--- app -> resources ->views->welcome.blade.php: Were  our home page route gets its view.


3) DATABASE:
		MIGRATIONS:
			--- database->migrations->2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table.php: Where you defined schema for the users table
					--> php artisan migrate : will use this schema to creat the users table structure.

